_json.description: Afghan Lamb in Cherry Sauce with rice and cauliflower  Your comments are welcome!  By Humaira                                                   It's not every day when lamb meets cherries in a pot. In the case of  today's recipe, Qorma e Aloo Baloo, the end result is a symphony of sweet  and sour delight for your taste buds.  After 33 years of living in the United States, I still remember cherry  season in Afghansitan, when my mom’s cousin would deliver boxes of cherries  to our home. Jeja, ...
